{"data": [{"id": "4747534", "title": "ISM Manufacturing Index Contracts For 9th Straight Month", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Currency and Exchange Stock Chart for Finance and Economy Display\" data-id=\"1358927461\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cemagraphics</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Jennifer Nash</em></p> <p>The Institute for Supply Management's (ISM) manufacturing purchasing managers' index (PMI) came in at 49.3 in December, higher than November's 48.4 reading, but keeping the index in contraction territory for the 9th straight month. The manufacturing sector has now contracted for 25 of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358927461/image_1358927461.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747534-ism-manufacturing-index-contracts-for-9th-straight-month", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 23:10:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747510", "title": "An Emerging Big Dividend AI Opportunity: TC Energy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money pouring out of a pipe\" data-id=\"91830572\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8000px\" height=\"5000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">canakat</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>2024 was a huge year for the energy infrastructure sector (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MLPX\" title=\"Global X MLP &amp; Energy Infrastructure ETF\">MLPX</a>), largely driven by the growing recognition by Mr. Market that well-located, high-quality energy infrastructure assets will be invaluable during the AI boom, as natural gas in particular will be</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/91830572/image_91830572.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747510-an-emerging-big-dividend-ai-opportunity-tc-energy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 23:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747526", "title": "United Airlines: Big 2025 Ahead", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial planning 2025 concept\" data-id=\"1886161065\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1097px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886161065/image_1886161065.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) cal