.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">ryasick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>BlackRock TCP Capital Corp. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TCPC\" title=\"BlackRock TCP Capital Corp\">TCPC</a></span>) in its current form originated from the merger between BlackRock TCP Capital and BlackRock Capital Investment in the first-quarter of FY 2024. The BDC, unfortunately, has seen a significant increase in its non-accrual percentage, which rose to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747525-blackrock-tcp-capital-the-tide-is-turning-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 22:42:07", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747523", "title": "Haverty Furniture Companies: Not Cheap Enough For An Upgrade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1190446487/image_1190446487.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Haverty\"s Furniture storefront-Pineville' data-id=\"1190446487\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6389px\" height=\"4480px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1190446487/image_1190446487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1190446487/image_1190446487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280