igure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Busy traffic at dusk on the M42 Motorway near Birmingham\" data-id=\"155385262\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1068px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">esp_imaging/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Rekor Systems Overview</h2> <p>The sharp rise in the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SP500</a>) in 2024 was attributed mostly to the \u201cMagnificent 7\u201d stocks, which form a huge chunk of the index. But as 2025 begins and these momentum stocks sell</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747524-rekor-systems-undeniable-momentum-in-this-under-recognized-tech-vendor", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 22:20:22", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747506", "title": "Undercovered Dozen: Natera, Lloyds Banking Group, Eaton, Primoris Services +", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Beautiful light for celebration of Festive colorful fireworks display on night sky, isolated on black background\" data-id=\"2184036626\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1239px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">boonsom/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Undercovered Dozen Introduction</h2> <p><em>The 'Undercovered' Dozen</em> is a weekly Seeking Alpha editor-curated series highlighting 12 articles on lesser covered stocks from the previous seven days. We hope this provides ideas and inspires discussion.</p> <p>Today, we're looking</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747506-undercovered-dozen-natera-lloyds-banking-group-eaton-primoris-services-plus", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 22:00:02", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747516", "title": "MSC Industrial Hit Hard By Operating Deleverage During This Downturn", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/554900097/photo/steel-worker-cutting-steel-items-at-factory.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=7wzHMCrWucb5Wr3AHamIRj3S4fhIivqs6Ii9Lg-Ds30=\" alt=\"Steel worker cutting steel items at factory\" data-id=\"554900097\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There\u2019s not a lot of good news yet in short-cycle manufacturing, and that\u2019s bad news for leading metalworking distributor <strong>MSC Industrial </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSM\" title=\"MSC Industrial Direct Co., Inc.\">MSM</a></span>). Not only has MSC Industrial\u2019s sales performance been lagging broader industrial</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747516-msc-industrial-hit-hard-by-operating-deleverage-during-this-downturn", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 21:30:48", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747512", "titl